com.google.openbidder.api.interceptor

Class RequestReceiver<C extends InterceptorController<?,?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.openbidder.api.interceptor.RequestReceiver<C>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HttpReceiver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BidRequestReceiver, ClickRequestReceiver, ImpressionRequestReceiver, MatchRequestReceiver

    public abstract class RequestReceiver<C extends InterceptorController<?,?>>
extends Object
implements HttpReceiver
    Basic request receiver: the object that takes care of all transport-neutral activities to handle some kind of request. Subclasses may extend functionality for different types of requests, and/or for particular needs of specific exchanges.
